\id PSA  
\h Psalms 
\toc1 Manikay mala 
\toc3 Psalms 
\toc2 Psalms 
\mt1 Manikay mala  
\c 46  
\p
\v 1 Banha ŋalma bayiŋ marim warraṯthun, nhanmam ŋarru Godthum ŋalmaliny guŋga’yun bitjanna bili. Ŋarram ŋalma bayiŋ banha nhanguḻ, bili nhän banha ŋalmaliŋgu ŋurrwum’ ga nhän bayiŋ banha ŋalmaliny wanyuyumanma.   